title: Birthday Poro Icon
body: I got Riot Kayle but still havent received the Icon, are the icons still being carried out?

replies.body: The icons are still being sent out, fear not!  Stay up to date on our [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) as there are a lot of players and will take some time.  Patience, you'll get the goods! :D
